  <entry>
    <title>移除 PPT 母版页背景图片</title>
    <url>/archives/aadd7006.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="解决方案"><a href="#解决方案" class="headerlink" title="解决方案"></a>解决方案</h1><p>右键点击【设置背景格式】<a id="more"></a></p>
<p><img src="/archives/aadd7006/image-20200529135952011.png" alt></p>
<p>勾选 【隐藏背景图片】，并点击【应用到全部】</p>
<p><img src="/archives/aadd7006/image-20200529140054874.png" alt></p>
<p><img src="/archives/aadd7006/C:%5CUsers%5CJulia%5CAppData%5CRoaming%5CTypora%5Ctypora-user-images%5Cimage-20200529140211204.png" alt></p>
<p>切换至【视图】，选择【幻灯片母版】</p>
<p><img src="/archives/aadd7006/image-20200529140327015.png" alt></p>
<p>选取左侧边栏幻灯片大纲的顶层第一张，并点击【背景样式】</p>
<p><img src="/archives/aadd7006/image-20200529140648625.png" alt></p>
<p>选择白色背景，可以看到母版页的背景都变成了白色</p>
<p><img src="/archives/aadd7006/image-20200529140735928.png" alt></p>
]]></content>
